{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.1","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:1","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.028.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">\u00c9z\u00e9chias, roi de Juda<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-19: cf. 2 R 18:1-6. 2 Ch 34:1-10. \u00c9s 52:1. Jn 1:48; 2:17.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\u00c9z\u00e9chias devint roi \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e2ge de vingt-cinq ans, et il r\u00e9gna vingt-neuf ans \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem. Sa m\u00e8re s\u2019appelait Abija, fille de Zacharie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.2","name":"2 Chroniques 29:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.28.27","name":"2 Chroniques 28:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.28.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.2","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:2","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il fit ce qui est droit aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, enti\u00e8rement comme avait fait David, son p\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.3","name":"2 Chroniques 29:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.1","name":"2 Chroniques 29:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.3","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:3","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>La premi\u00e8re ann\u00e9e de son r\u00e8gne, au premier mois, il ouvrit les portes de la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et il les r\u00e9para.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.4","name":"2 Chroniques 29:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.2","name":"2 Chroniques 29:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.4","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:4","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Il fit venir les sacrificateurs et les L\u00e9vites, qu\u2019il assembla dans la place orientale,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.5","name":"2 Chroniques 29:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.3","name":"2 Chroniques 29:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.5","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:5","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>et il leur dit: \u00c9coutez-moi, L\u00e9vites! Maintenant sanctifiez-vous, sanctifiez la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu de vos p\u00e8res, et mettez ce qui est impur hors du sanctuaire.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.6","name":"2 Chroniques 29:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.4","name":"2 Chroniques 29:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.6","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:6","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Car nos p\u00e8res ont p\u00e9ch\u00e9, ils ont fait ce qui est mal aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, notre Dieu, ils l\u2019ont abandonn\u00e9, ils ont d\u00e9tourn\u00e9 leurs regards du tabernacle de l\u2019\u00c9ternel et lui ont tourn\u00e9 le dos.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.7","name":"2 Chroniques 29:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.5","name":"2 Chroniques 29:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.7","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:7","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Ils ont m\u00eame ferm\u00e9 les portes du portique et \u00e9teint les lampes, et ils n\u2019ont offert au Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl ni parfums ni holocaustes dans le sanctuaire.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.8","name":"2 Chroniques 29:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.6","name":"2 Chroniques 29:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.8","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:8","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Aussi la col\u00e8re de l\u2019\u00c9ternel a \u00e9t\u00e9 sur Juda et sur J\u00e9rusalem, et il les a livr\u00e9s au trouble, \u00e0 la d\u00e9solation et \u00e0 la moquerie, comme vous le voyez de vos yeux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.9","name":"2 Chroniques 29:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.7","name":"2 Chroniques 29:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.9","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:9","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Et voici, \u00e0 cause de cela nos p\u00e8res sont tomb\u00e9s par l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e, et nos fils, nos filles et nos femmes sont en captivit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.10","name":"2 Chroniques 29:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.8","name":"2 Chroniques 29:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.10","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:10","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>J\u2019ai donc l\u2019intention de faire alliance avec l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, pour que son ardente col\u00e8re se d\u00e9tourne de nous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.11","name":"2 Chroniques 29:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.9","name":"2 Chroniques 29:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.11","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:11","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Maintenant, mes fils, cessez d\u2019\u00eatre n\u00e9gligents; car vous avez \u00e9t\u00e9 choisis par l\u2019\u00c9ternel pour vous tenir \u00e0 son service devant lui, pour \u00eatre ses serviteurs, et pour lui offrir des parfums.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.12","name":"2 Chroniques 29:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.10","name":"2 Chroniques 29:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.12","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:12","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Et les L\u00e9vites se lev\u00e8rent: Machath, fils d\u2019Amasa\u00ef, Jo\u00ebl, fils d\u2019Azaria, des fils des Kehathites; et des fils des Merarites, Kis, fils d\u2019Abdi, Azaria, fils de Jehall\u00e9leel; et des Guerschonites, Joach, fils de Zimma, \u00c9den, fils de Joach;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.13","name":"2 Chroniques 29:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.11","name":"2 Chroniques 29:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.13","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:13","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>et des fils d\u2019\u00c9litsaphan, Schimri et Je\u00efel; et des fils d\u2019Asaph, Zacharie et Matthania;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.14","name":"2 Chroniques 29:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.12","name":"2 Chroniques 29:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.14","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:14","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>et des fils d\u2019H\u00e9man, Jehiel et Schime\u00ef; et des fils de Jeduthun, Schemaeja et Uzziel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.15","name":"2 Chroniques 29:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.13","name":"2 Chroniques 29:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.15","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:15","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Ils r\u00e9unirent leurs fr\u00e8res, et, apr\u00e8s s\u2019\u00eatre sanctifi\u00e9s, ils vinrent pour purifier la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, selon l\u2019ordre du roi et d\u2019apr\u00e8s les paroles de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.16","name":"2 Chroniques 29:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.14","name":"2 Chroniques 29:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.16","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:16","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Les sacrificateurs entr\u00e8rent dans l\u2019int\u00e9rieur de la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel pour la purifier; ils sortirent toutes les impuret\u00e9s qu\u2019ils trouv\u00e8rent dans le temple de l\u2019\u00c9ternel et les mirent dans le parvis de la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, o\u00f9 les L\u00e9vites les re\u00e7urent pour les emporter dehors au torrent de C\u00e9dron.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.17","name":"2 Chroniques 29:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.15","name":"2 Chroniques 29:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.17","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:17","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Ils commenc\u00e8rent ces purifications le premier jour du premier mois; le huiti\u00e8me jour du mois, ils entr\u00e8rent dans le portique de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et ils mirent huit jours \u00e0 purifier la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel; le seizi\u00e8me jour du premier mois, ils avaient achev\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.18","name":"2 Chroniques 29:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.16","name":"2 Chroniques 29:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.18","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:18","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Ils se rendirent ensuite chez le roi \u00c9z\u00e9chias, et dirent: Nous avons purifi\u00e9 toute la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, l\u2019autel des holocaustes et tous ses ustensiles, et la table des pains de proposition et tous ses ustensiles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.19","name":"2 Chroniques 29:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.17","name":"2 Chroniques 29:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.19","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:19","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Nous avons remis en \u00e9tat et purifi\u00e9 tous les ustensiles que le roi Achaz avait profan\u00e9s pendant son r\u00e8gne, lors de ses transgressions: ils sont devant l\u2019autel de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.20","name":"2 Chroniques 29:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.18","name":"2 Chroniques 29:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.20","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:20","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.021,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Le temple purifi\u00e9 et le culte r\u00e9tabli<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 20-36: cf. L\u00e9 9. Esd 6:16-18. Mal 3:4.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Le roi \u00c9z\u00e9chias se leva de bon matin, assembla les chefs de la ville, et monta \u00e0 la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.21","name":"2 Chroniques 29:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.19","name":"2 Chroniques 29:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.21","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:21","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Ils offrirent sept taureaux, sept b\u00e9liers, sept agneaux et sept boucs, en sacrifice d\u2019expiation pour le royaume, pour le sanctuaire, et pour Juda. Le roi ordonna aux sacrificateurs, fils d\u2019Aaron, de les offrir sur l\u2019autel de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.22","name":"2 Chroniques 29:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.20","name":"2 Chroniques 29:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.22","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:22","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Les sacrificateurs \u00e9gorg\u00e8rent les b\u0153ufs, et re\u00e7urent le sang, qu\u2019ils r\u00e9pandirent sur l\u2019autel; ils \u00e9gorg\u00e8rent les b\u00e9liers, et r\u00e9pandirent le sang sur l\u2019autel; ils \u00e9gorg\u00e8rent les agneaux, et r\u00e9pandirent le sang sur l\u2019autel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.23","name":"2 Chroniques 29:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.21","name":"2 Chroniques 29:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.23","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:23","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>On amena ensuite les boucs expiatoires devant le roi et devant l\u2019assembl\u00e9e, qui pos\u00e8rent leurs mains sur eux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.24","name":"2 Chroniques 29:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.22","name":"2 Chroniques 29:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.24","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:24","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Les sacrificateurs les \u00e9gorg\u00e8rent, et r\u00e9pandirent leur sang au pied de l\u2019autel en expiation pour les p\u00e9ch\u00e9s de tout Isra\u00ebl; car c\u2019\u00e9tait pour tout Isra\u00ebl que le roi avait ordonn\u00e9 l\u2019holocauste et le sacrifice d\u2019expiation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.25","name":"2 Chroniques 29:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.23","name":"2 Chroniques 29:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.25","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:25","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Il fit placer les L\u00e9vites dans la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel avec des cymbales, des luths et des harpes, selon l\u2019ordre de David, de Gad le voyant du roi, et de Nathan, le proph\u00e8te; car c\u2019\u00e9tait un ordre de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, transmis par ses proph\u00e8tes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.26","name":"2 Chroniques 29:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.24","name":"2 Chroniques 29:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.26","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:26","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Les L\u00e9vites prirent place avec les instruments de David, et les sacrificateurs avec les trompettes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.27","name":"2 Chroniques 29:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.25","name":"2 Chroniques 29:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.27","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:27","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>\u00c9z\u00e9chias ordonna d\u2019offrir l\u2019holocauste sur l\u2019autel; et au moment o\u00f9 commen\u00e7a l\u2019holocauste, commen\u00e7a aussi le chant de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, au son des trompettes et avec accompagnement des instruments de David, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.28","name":"2 Chroniques 29:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.26","name":"2 Chroniques 29:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.28","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:28","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Toute l\u2019assembl\u00e9e se prosterna, on chanta le cantique, et l\u2019on sonna des trompettes, le tout jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que l\u2019holocauste f\u00fbt achev\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.27","name":"2 Chroniques 29:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.29","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:29","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Et quand on eut achev\u00e9 d\u2019offrir l\u2019holocauste, le roi et tous ceux qui \u00e9taient avec lui fl\u00e9chirent le genou et se prostern\u00e8rent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.30","name":"2 Chroniques 29:30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.28","name":"2 Chroniques 29:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.30","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:30","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Puis le roi \u00c9z\u00e9chias et les chefs dirent aux L\u00e9vites de c\u00e9l\u00e9brer l\u2019\u00c9ternel avec les paroles de David et du proph\u00e8te Asaph; et ils le c\u00e9l\u00e9br\u00e8rent avec des transports de joie, et ils s\u2019inclin\u00e8rent et se prostern\u00e8rent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.31","name":"2 Chroniques 29:31","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.31","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:31","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>\u00c9z\u00e9chias prit alors la parole, et dit: Maintenant que vous vous \u00eates consacr\u00e9s \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, approchez-vous, amenez des victimes et offrez en sacrifices d\u2019actions de gr\u00e2ces \u00e0 la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel. Et l\u2019assembl\u00e9e amena des victimes et offrit des sacrifices d\u2019actions de gr\u00e2ces, et tous ceux dont le c\u0153ur \u00e9tait bien dispos\u00e9 offrirent des holocaustes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.32","name":"2 Chroniques 29:32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.30","name":"2 Chroniques 29:30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.32","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:32","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Le nombre des holocaustes offerts par l\u2019assembl\u00e9e fut de soixante-dix b\u0153ufs, cent b\u00e9liers, et deux cents agneaux; toutes ces victimes furent immol\u00e9es en holocauste \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.33","name":"2 Chroniques 29:33","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.31","name":"2 Chroniques 29:31","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.33","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:33","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Et l\u2019on consacra encore six cents b\u0153ufs et trois mille brebis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.34","name":"2 Chroniques 29:34","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.32","name":"2 Chroniques 29:32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.34","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:34","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Mais les sacrificateurs \u00e9taient en petit nombre, et ils ne purent d\u00e9pouiller tous les holocaustes; leurs fr\u00e8res, les L\u00e9vites, les aid\u00e8rent jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que l\u2019ouvrage f\u00fbt fini, et jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que les autres sacrificateurs se fussent sanctifi\u00e9s, car les L\u00e9vites avaient eu plus \u00e0 c\u0153ur de se sanctifier que les sacrificateurs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.35","name":"2 Chroniques 29:35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.33","name":"2 Chroniques 29:33","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.35","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:35","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.029.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>Il y avait d\u2019ailleurs beaucoup d\u2019holocaustes, avec les graisses des sacrifices d\u2019actions de gr\u00e2ces, et avec les libations des holocaustes. Ainsi fut r\u00e9tabli le service de la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.36","name":"2 Chroniques 29:36","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.34","name":"2 Chroniques 29:34","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.36","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 29:36","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.029.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.030.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.29.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>\u00c9z\u00e9chias et tout le peuple se r\u00e9jouirent de ce que Dieu avait bien dispos\u00e9 le peuple, car la chose se fit subitement.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29","name":"2 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.30.1","name":"2 Chroniques 30:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.30.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.29.35","name":"2 Chroniques 29:35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.29.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb5dc69a0.47269896');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb5dc69a0.47269896\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb5dc69a0.47269896","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb5dc69a0.47269896'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb5dc69a0.47269896\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}